# Calc Calories Project Instructions

## Language
ВСЕГДА отвечать на русском языке. Все объяснения, комментарии и общение должны быть на русском языке.
Для сообщений в git комитах используй English.

## Project Overview
This is a Next.js application for tracking and calculating calories with authentication.

## Tech Stack
- Next.js (App Router)
- TypeScript
- Shadcn for built-in components
- NextAuth.js for authentication
- Tailwind CSS for styling

## Development Guidelines
- Use "mobile first" approach 
- Use TypeScript for all new files
- Follow Next.js App Router conventions
- Place components in `src/components/`
- Use absolute imports when possible
- Implement proper error handling
- Ensure responsive design

## Project Structure
- `src/app/` - Next.js app router pages and layouts
- `src/components/` - Reusable React components
- `src/app/api/` - API routes
- `public/` - Static assets

## Authentication
- Using NextAuth.js for authentication
- Auth provider is configured in `src/app/auth-provider.tsx`
- Sign in/out components are in `src/components/`

## Code Style
- Use functional components with hooks
- Prefer arrow functions for components
- Use proper TypeScript types
- Follow ESLint and Prettier configurations
- Write descriptive commit messages

## When making changes:
1. Always check existing code patterns first
2. Maintain consistency with current architecture
3. Add proper TypeScript types
4. Test authentication flows if modifying auth
5. Ensure mobile responsiveness
